<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I would like to car=
ry on with our provided process and have the upstairs cleaned and the gib-b=
oard wall linings removed to enable us to inspect the exterior wall cavitie=
s to complete a thorough assessment
 of the repairs required. Can I have your approval to instruct Davids team =
to do so?<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
