<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
libri&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning Rafael=
la,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As per the next pha=
se of the process map =E2=80=93 Stephen Walker from ASURNZ =E2=80=93 our Te=
chnical Building Consultant is due to visit site and author the scope of wo=
rks required.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stephen and I will =
be visiting site at<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>12=
:30 today</u><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to complete=
 the walk-through and determine the scope-of-works
 for the repairs to your home.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Once we have comple=
ted this document =E2=80=93 I can return and go through each item on the sc=
ope line-by-line in detail with you so you can gain the confidence that we =
have captured everything.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">When we go through =
the scope together =E2=80=93 we can consider adding anything further that i=
s necessary if we need to. I am exceptionally confident that Stephen and I =
will capture everything on the first draft =E2=80=93
 but I want you to know that you will sign-off on the scope-of-works as bei=
ng complete before we move to the repair phase.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You do not need to =
join us for today=E2=80=99s visit =E2=80=93 but you are more than welcome t=
o if you wish. As I stated =E2=80=93 we can review it together once complet=
e. I will let you decide whether you wish to join us or not.</span><o:p></o=
:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please do not hesit=
ate to contact me if you have any questions or concerns at all.</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.<span class=
=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
